02:08.940 --> 02:10.300
Il ne vous a pas importunée ?

02:10.300 --> 02:10.940
homme ivre

02:11.940 --> 02:12.780
importuner

02:13.810 --> 02:14.380
Non

02:15.380 --> 02:15.890
Tant mieux

02:16.340 --> 02:17.060
La nuit

02:17.060 --> 02:18.250
